<br>
As for most important, I think Clerics of course.  But to be honest, I think the reason clerics are so important is rez.  A Cleric with clicker is more important than a cleric without.  Complete heal is important for MA, but if the raid is working properly, the rest of the groups can get by with druids, shaman, or paladins doing the healing. <p>Buddhist monk says to the hotdog vender, "make me one with everything."<br>
